This file contains the CHANGELOG (version history) of the BreadCrumbs extension.

* v0.6.1 - 2018-10-08
  - Removed dependencies on globals $wgUser and $wgRequest
  - Removed compatibility code for 1.18.0 that had been obsolete since 2016 (change 328894)

* v0.6.0 - 2018-06-10
  - Converted to use extension registration
  - Minor style fixes

* v0.5.0 - 2017-07-17
  - Remove I18n shim

* v0.4.1 - 2016-03-18
  - Add license lable to show on "Special:Version"
  - Fix "typos" in the LICENSE file
  - Fix style position warnings
  - Switch to consitently use DIR

* v0.4.0 - 2014-03-30
  - Migrate to JSON i18n

* v0.3.0 - 2012-06-26
  - Began to restrict options for better administration
  - Provided loading for CSS, instructions for overriding CSS

* v0.2.1 - 2012-06-14
  - Exposed a variety of options to the user in "Special:Preferences"
  - Provided advanced logic for breadcrumb creation/handling

* v0.2.0 - 2012-06-12
  - fixed breadcrumb uniqueness checker
  - removed CSS file, replaced with in-wiki formatting
  - Checked for use of deprecated wiki functions

* v0.1.0 - 2007-03-21
  - first working version
  - added CSS file
  - restructured
